{"tid":2005750,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"對中共與WHO咎責！美議員：拒買中國貨是最有力的懲罰","createTime":"2020-05-07T10:16:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T13:51:18.000Z","uid":141151,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f6bb0b3f6aa3b259a23aaa8054675952415351ce","tid":2005750,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:16:01.000Z","msg":"對中共與WHO咎責！美議員：拒買中國貨是最有力的懲罰<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3157919\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3157919&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdZ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=1450c92f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3157919&h=43fb7539\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3157919</a><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕美國共和黨參議員史考特（Rick Scott）週三接受《福斯新聞》採訪指出，他將挖掘武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒疾病，COVID-19）爆發背後的真相，並對中國及WHO的不當行為進行咎責，其中最有力的懲罰方式就是拒買中國貨。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">《福斯新聞》報導，做為美國國土安全委員會一員的史考特，將領導團隊調查WHO及中國。由於在疫情大流行期間，WHO多次為中國防疫不力的行為進行辯護，受到全球廣大批評。<br />\n<br />\n史考特直指，WHO根本是中共的傀儡，不把他人的利益放在心上，但美國目前對WHO的懲罰並未改變任何事情，譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus）尚未感受到壓力。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n就史考特目前對WHO掌握的資訊，他認為，這個組職顯然還有一些技術資訊尚未公開，因此他們將釐清病毒起源，調查病毒是否是被創造或散佈出來的，但無論結果是起源於野味市場或是實驗室，這當中最糟糕的一點是，他們不願向世界據實以告，來自中國的數字亦不準確。<br />\n<br />\n史考特認為，美國要對中國在疫情中行為咎責，最有力的反擊方式就是拒絕與中共進行貿易，停止購買中國的商品貨物，他說：「中國偷了我們的工作機會與相關技術，現在他們又故意引起事端扼殺美國人的就業，這對美國、歐洲及全球的人們都是受害者。」<br />\n<br />\n史考特指出，他在去年提出1項法案，目前看來有望通過，此法案將規定線上經銷商，必須揭露各項產品的製造產地；史考特還有另外1項提案，將增加美國製造的庫存，減少對中國的依賴，並為下次的大流行做好準備。"},{"pid":"3a72b56b493e5de8b17b431cd998fb748656f8ee","tid":2005750,"uid":3776,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:21:03.000Z","msg":"最強大既黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96cbaeb854cbb07b401aa55f484a85fca33bd8e8","tid":2005750,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:30:04.000Z","msg":"iphone？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abbc6147dc50eb91c5ba3d8b283d3f6c5c9ebd5f","tid":2005750,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:31:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d2a7e12aeb548680a4c31940c502ad08f0b514a","tid":2005750,"uid":251732,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:32:09.000Z","msg":"倒不如搞掂美國內部嘅親中分子先講啦？<br />\n 萬一china Joe做總統嘅話，佢一定會當冇事發生過"},{"pid":"c1ba41d76c8cd4a65970375f9982c183fbd63ff3","tid":2005750,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:35:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adbdf57ff013360a486abd35b44f669e9626fe8f","tid":2005750,"uid":22701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:36:19.000Z","msg":"係時候搵人推國際黃色經濟圈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f9a1f72ac635381ca0a34246b64795fec796d2f","tid":2005750,"uid":90183,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:36:48.000Z","msg":"國際級黃色經濟體"},{"pid":"074437b5bc746677a14b395451bc1077432e070b","tid":2005750,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4966c7149177e67cdd000abffc91012e73a14051","tid":2005750,"uid":83251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:37:25.000Z","msg":"直接出兵打鳩支那最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f4e1e54c27026f7fedf